Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:12.00,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}翻译/校对/时间轴：海底  后期：小圣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:13.00,zhu,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:36.55,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(800,0)}強くなれる理由を知った
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:44.73,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕を連れて　進め
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:52.86,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泥だらけの走馬灯に酔う
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:57.57,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強張る心　震える手は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:00:59.95,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}掴みたいものがある
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:01.74,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それだけさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:05.33,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夜の匂いに(I’ll spend all thirty nights)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:08.88,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}空睨んでも (Staring into the sky)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:14.05,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}変わっていけるのは　自分自身だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:16.05,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それだけさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:22.81,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強くなれる理由を知った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:29.19,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕を連れて　進め
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:34.03,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうしたって消せない夢も　止まれない今も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:38.32,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰かのために強くなれるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:43.37,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何度でも立ち上がれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:48.04,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}世界に打ちのめされて　守る意味を知った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:52.59,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}紅蓮の華よ　咲き誇れ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:57.88,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}運命を照らして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:57.88,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:36.55,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(800,0)}知晓了为何能变强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:44.73,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}与我携手 前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:52.86,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沉醉于遍布泥土的走马灯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:57.57,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}顽固的心 颤抖的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:00:59.95,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为有想紧握之物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:01.74,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:05.33,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在夜的气息中{\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr5 B-KL\fs40\fsp0}(I’ll spend all thirty nights)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:08.88,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}久久凝视天空{\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr5 B-KL\fs40\fsp0}(Staring into the sky)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:14.05,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能够改变的 却只有自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:16.05,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:22.81,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知晓了为何能变强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:29.19,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}与我携手 前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:34.03,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}挥之不去的梦境 无法阻挡的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:38.32,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要能为那个人而变强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:43.37,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不论多少次 都要重新振作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:48.04,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被世界摧毁 知晓了守护之意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:52.59,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}红莲之花 骄傲绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:57.88,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}将命运照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:01:59.84,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:39.61,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(691,300)}悲しみに囚われたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:48.95,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}俯いた場所に涙を落として行きたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:52.20,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}運命を振りほどいて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:58.17,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}走り出せるはずなんだ　願いは叶うはずなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:22:01.54,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,0)}叩き潰せ　昨日の葛藤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.54,0:22:06.84,ed-jp,,0,0,5,,{\blur2}cry for the future from the edge of darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:13.35,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}向かい風を乗っ取って　嵐の先は見えなくたって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:18.27,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}もう道は選べない　勝ち残れ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.27,0:22:26.11,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}迷いはいつも愛情と怒りを秤にかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:33.16,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(0,500)}さあ　立ち上がるんだ　もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:47.13,ed-jp,,0,0,3,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}今　君はその刃を　どこへ振り下ろす？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:20.08,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:39.61,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(691,300)}不愿在悲伤之中迷失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:48.95,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}不愿在倒下之处落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:52.20,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}无视命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:58.17,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}定能勇往直前 定能实现梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:22:01.54,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,0)}斩断昨日纠葛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.54,0:22:06.84,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}cry for the future from the edge of darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:13.35,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}驭风而行 即便被风暴遮蔽前路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:18.27,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也只能前进 战胜强敌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.27,0:22:26.11,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}踌躇之时 总在爱恨间摇摆不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:33.16,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(0,500)}再一次站起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:47.13,ed-cn,,0,0,3,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}此刻 你会将那刀刃 挥向何方？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:49.18,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,炭治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼杀队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可不是玩乐的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你这种垃圾就该被肃清
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻肃清
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,别给我小看鬼杀队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,祢豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,祢豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,祢豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,祢豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,善逸 你别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,炭治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们好好相处吧 炭治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,善逸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我求你了 别缠着我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:54.11,zhu,,0,0,0,,炭治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,别说这种话嘛 炭治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,祢豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,炭治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:02.70,zhu,,0,0,0,,别这样 善逸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,祢豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:05.08,zhu,,0,0,0,,炭治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:06.45,zhu,,0,0,0,,祢豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.84,zhu,,0,0,0,,善逸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,您的衣服好像很脏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我会给您洗干净的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,请先换上这件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这衣服触感很好 穿着很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,晚饭吃天妇罗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对 是那个裹着一层面粉的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,祢豆子 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你安静点 伊之助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,炭治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:20.03,biaoti,,0,0,0,,{\pos(886.667,386.667)\c&H0802B3&\fad(981,0)}那田蜘蛛山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,痊愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,北北东 北北东
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个目的地是北北东
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,三人一起去那田蜘蛛山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,去那田蜘蛛山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢您的关照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我来给各位打火驱邪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你搞什么啊 老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,她在打火 帮我们驱邪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们的工作很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不论何时 都请务必自豪地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,祝各位好运
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,自豪？ 好运？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这人什么都不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想 被这么一问还真回答不上来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,充分理解自己的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,言行举止要得当 不让自己的立场蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,然后老奶奶还在祈祷我们平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,什么立场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不让自己的立场蒙羞又是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,得当的言行举止 具体要怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么老太婆要祈祷我们平安无事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,她明明跟我们没有任何关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那老太婆没有理解自己的立场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,能等一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,善逸 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,快到目的地了 我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙坐在地上干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我好意思说我啊 野猪头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,眼前那座山 你们什么都没感觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是坐在这种地方也无济于事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,果然恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我很正常 你们才异常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么气味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,炭治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不要丢下我一个人 不要丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,救 救命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,穿着队服 是鬼杀队员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我也被连上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我先去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你就边发抖边跟在我后面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子咕咕叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,伊之助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是跃跃欲试才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,蜘蛛网
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,到处都是蜘蛛网啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,伊之助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你说要一起来 让我安心了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,山里传来一股扭曲的邪恶气息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点被吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这衣服触感很好 穿着很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不论何时 都请务必自豪地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,祝各位好运
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,伊之助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来支援你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我是癸阶剑士 灶门炭治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,癸阶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,癸阶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不是柱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,癸阶来多少人都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,伊之助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,要说意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你的存在才没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快给我说明情况 弱鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这人什么情况啊 明明我才是前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,鎹 鎹鸦传来了指令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,十个队员一起来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,进山后不久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,队员就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,队员开始自相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子们几乎都被干掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那里说不定有十二鬼月
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,看来必须派柱去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,义勇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,人和鬼要是能和睦相处就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,富冈 你不觉得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,只要鬼还吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这就不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是被讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一般来说 会把人家丢下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,把同伴 丢在路边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,既然是同伴 就不劝劝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们两个一起劝我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:23.67,zhu,,0,0,0,,善逸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:25.34,zhu,,0,0,0,,善逸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是我 也还是会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可那两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一溜烟跑进那座恐怖的山里了 头也不回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,也不为我这个被抛弃的人想想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:47.15,pm1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1205,368)\fad(231,0)}唉声叹气也没用 快点去帮助同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真羡慕你 这么轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本就不了解人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是这种地方一点都不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一丁点都不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,祢豆子明明是鬼 都那么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你身为麻雀 也太凶暴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙带着祢豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么把我亲爱的祢豆子给带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,炭治郎真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,别把女孩子带到危险的地方去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,祢豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,又听到这声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就是在听到这个声音之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,队员们才开始自相残杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,声音是从哪里传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这些家伙都是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不知道队员之间打架是违规的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 他们的动作不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他们被操纵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那就砍了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,还活着 里面有人还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 不能伤害同伴的遗骸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:17:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,别总是否定我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,背后有甜香味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,气味很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他们被丝操纵了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,把丝砍断
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我在你之前就发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,操纵他们的鬼在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么 好刺鼻的臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然只有一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,蜘蛛在牵丝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我可爱的人偶们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,疯狂起舞吧 直到手脚断掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只砍丝没用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,蜘蛛会再次牵丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,又是刺鼻的臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这什么啊 随着风飘过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那把这些蜘蛛杀光就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,蜘蛛很小 而且估计数量众多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,必须找到操纵它们的鬼才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没用的 伊之助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,伊之助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你拥有判明鬼的位置的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就帮帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才开始就总是闻到奇怪的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我的鼻子没法发挥作用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 你叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫村田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,村田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我和村田一起拖住被操纵的队员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,伊之助 你就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,别妨碍我们一家人的平静生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,浮在空中？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 他站在了丝上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一家人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,反正妈妈很快就会杀掉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你小子去哪里 跟我决斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,伊之助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他是来做什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他应该不是操纵丝的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所以首先…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,要找出鬼的位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,烦死了 额头太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,兽之呼吸 柒之型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,空间识觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不会让任何人来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一家五口要幸福地生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的羁绊 无人能斩断
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,祢豆子 炭治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.15,0:23:09.28,pm1-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1029.333,359.667)}你先冷静下来 听听周围的声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.20,0:23:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,祢豆子有危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你别叫了 来一起找啊 啾太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:13.91,pm1-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1061.333,348.667)}都说要你冷静了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:16.41,pm1-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1061.333,348.667)}现在开始 大正传闻悄悄话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:18.54,pm1-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1029.333,370)}我真正的名字是『五加』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:20.87,pm1-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1029.333,370)}因为我很喜欢吃五加饭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:23.08,pm1-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1029.333,370)}但善逸一直不知道 只给我吃豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,给你吃这个 冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:28.67,pm1-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1061.333,348.667)}是五加饭做的饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,吃完你也要好好找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,祢豆子陷入危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:32.47,pm1-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1061.333,371.334)}真的在担心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:34.18,pm1-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1030.667,370.667)}就因为这样 他才让人讨厌不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,祢豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 第16集 不让自己 而让别人站在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.89,0:23:40.06,zhu,,0,0,0,,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
